201
00:16:12,190 --> 00:16:14,830
Medyo naiintindihan ko na.

202
00:16:18,950 --> 00:16:26,280
Napakasakit
kapag ang puso mo ay parang impiyerno.

203
00:16:31,070 --> 00:16:34,670
Pagkababa ng department store,

204
00:16:34,670 --> 00:16:37,940
Naging pabigat ako sa mga anak ko.

205
00:16:37,940 --> 00:16:42,420
Ako, si Han Gi Bok, ay wala kung wala ang aking pagmamataas.

206
00:16:45,460 --> 00:16:48,310
It's hell, Eun Hye.

207
00:16:56,390 --> 00:16:58,830
Matapos akong iwan ng ganoon,

208
00:17:01,200 --> 00:17:04,320
masaya ka ba dyan?

209
00:17:05,430 --> 00:17:07,300
Ama!

210
00:17:15,390 --> 00:17:18,830
Anong ginagawa mo dito?

211
00:17:18,830 --> 00:17:21,030
Paano mo nalaman na nandito ako?

212
00:17:21,030 --> 00:17:25,670
Kung gusto mong pumunta dito, dapat
sinabi mo sa akin! Bakit palagi kang…

213
00:17:27,920 --> 00:17:30,060
pasensya na po.

214
00:17:30,060 --> 00:17:32,930
Hindi ko sinasadyang mag-alala ka.

215
00:17:34,300 --> 00:17:36,940
Gusto ko lang talagang sumama.

216
00:17:42,410 --> 00:17:44,060
pasensya na po.

217
00:17:49,820 --> 00:17:51,930
Paumanhin, Ama.

218
00:17:53,980 --> 00:17:57,800
Ako ay napakabata at tanga.

219
00:17:57,800 --> 00:18:00,820
Sa loob ng mahigit sampung taon, hindi kita naiintindihan

220
00:18:00,820 --> 00:18:04,460
at nagalit sayo. Ginawa kitang malungkot.

221
00:18:05,800 --> 00:18:07,760
pasensya na po.

222
00:18:14,940 --> 00:18:17,730
Bakit hindi mo sinabi sa akin?

223
00:18:18,940 --> 00:18:23,200
Bakit mo ako hinayaang galit sayo? Bakit? bakit...

224
00:18:30,760 --> 00:18:32,480
